_sText:
Fully planned Tspawn-Garage and Sewers...after that made it up as I went.  

Problems : Some clipping issue with items stuck into others and some textures need adjusting and will flesh out the map with some more props/ details for final version later on.

3D skybox will be looked into- still pretty new to SDK HAMMER  have to get on some tutorials.

I did included a labeled nav. mesh this time around though I didn't mess with the bot commands / path (dissapointed labels are set list and can't customize)

I went with darker coloration for light after complaints about de_canyon looking too bright and cartoonish.

Anyone wanna make a radar for me that'd be awesome lol I can try at some point.  Do not know anything about photo shop.   My wife has Photo Explosion version 4 I guess that counts as photoshop so maybe I'll be able to make a radar in the future.  I've glimpsed the tutorial on radar but ran away from it once got into all the photo shop stuff.

Anyways carrying on.  T-s enter sewers from garage/basement or sewer access in alley.  From the Sewers T's have 3 options  to Asite through side door area(connects to mid)  or to Middle / connects all other areas) or to siteB through tunnel and stairs area.  There is also an alt route beside mid that is accessed from middle or B sewers/ tunnel
